high_descs: Walk out of the office, make a left in the hallway, then a left into the kitchen, and walk over to the kitchen sink.
Pick up the spoon from the kitchen sink.
Walk over to the kitchen sink next to the faucet.
Place the spoon into the left hand side of the sink under the faucet, turn the water on then off, and then pick up the spoon again.
Turn around and walk over to the middle of the diningtable.
Place the spoon in the far right corner of the diningtable, near the wall.
anns.task_desc: Wash a spoon in the kitchen sink to place on the dining table.

high_descs: Turn and head towards the sink.
Pick the spoon near to the sink.
Turn around and head to the sink.
Put the spoon into the sink and pour the water and clean the spoon.
Take the cleaned spoon and turn left to reach the diningtable on your right.
Put the spoon on the diningtable.
anns.task_desc: Put the cleaned Spoon on the DiningTable.

high_descs: Turn around and walk to the sink.
Pick up the spoon from the table.
Turn around the spoon and put it in the sink.
Put the spoon in the washing basin to clean it.
Take the spoon from the diningtable and turn around the right side.
Put the spoon in the diningtable.
anns.task_desc: Take the spoon and put it on the dining table.
